snippet.title: Emilia Clarke REACTION Before Replacing Amber Heard in Aquaman 2!
snippet.description:
Emilia Clarke to REPLACE Amber Heard in Aquaman 2? | Amber Heard FIRED after Johnny Depp Drama

In the video Emilia Clarke speaks out about her possibly taking over for Amber Heard as a replacement In Aquaman 2!!!
During 2020 a lot of great comic book movies were delayed because of the world situation, but that is all about to change for 2021! Aquaman 2 is a potential movie that we might be getting to see in 2021 or at least in 2022, but after all of the drama between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, then Amber Heard has been removed as Mera in Aquaman 2, and the Game of Thrones idol Emilia Clarke might be the one to replace her!
